summary: A small cozy home in Falkreath!
descriptionHtml:
Description: 
*************

This is a small cozy home located inside Falkreath next to the cemetery. It has 1 double bed, 1 Mannequin, 1 Weapon Rack and Weapon Plaque. It is styled with upper class furniture not noble. This player home also has a trap door leading to a cellar and also a hidden entrance in Falkreath Cemetery.
Inside the home it also has a Alchemy table and Enchanting table in the cellar. It also comes with a cooking spit. You can find the key to the player home next to a tombstone in the cemetery. See images if you are having trouble locating it.

Installation:
*************
Drag Falkreathhome.esp to Skyrim\'s data folder and enjoy.

Uninstall: 

Delete Falkreathhome.esp from Skyrim\'s data folder.
